<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler und lieber <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Weykart, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von ewers
                                <expan>dien<ex>er</ex>s</expan> des Hellsmids und
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>Görg<ex>en</ex></expan> Hofmans <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.,
                        das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr edel <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        daz wir <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>Gorg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Hofma<ex>n</ex></expan> für uns besant und
                            <expan>sov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mit im davon gerett
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz er <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> selb sein antwurt schriftlich
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> tun sol. Wie
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> do <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir dem
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> diener von dem
                            <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> frewntlichs slewnigs
                            <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> umb sein zusprüch
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>geholff<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch im
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> schein<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit
                                <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        slewnigs <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> von dem
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add>hinfür</add>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim ist, on
                            <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. <expan>Bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                        edel mit fleiss, ir wellt den <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Hellsmid,
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> diener, unterrichten, daz er sich des
                                <expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan> lass. Das
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir umb ewr
                            <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> allczeit williklich und gern
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
